      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2340 - It has been narrated by Dawud Al-Raqqi from Abu Abdullah (as) that he said:\n\"When you have completed your rituals, then return, for it will make you more eager to come back.\""
